p: Prediction of proteins tertiary structure were done based on the amino acid sequences of the E protein of DENV-2 strain 43,248 using the protein homology/analogy recognition engine, version 2.0 [ 34]. The constructed structures were edited and visualized using the Jmol program, an open-source browser-based HTML5 viewer and stand-alone Java viewer for chemical structures in 3D ( https://www.jmol.org/) [ 35].
